[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "よし、あと調合が必要なのは……っと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00093",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "この目録にまとめたんでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00094",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、そうだった！　ありがと、ヤンネさん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00095",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "その目録、結構な量ですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_038_00096",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ん～？　これさ、ちょっと荷が多すぎない？\nこれだけあると、いざというときに動けないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00097",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うっ……やっぱそうっすかね。\n念には念を入れたんですけど、入れすぎか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00098",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "果ての大陸に続く道がある、暗黒の氷海――そこで\nアルビーナが死の恐怖に直面したってのは聞いたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00099",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん……アタシはあの海で一度、\n身の程を知らされた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00100",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でも、ヘルトに一泡吹かせた今のアルビちゃんは\nちょっと違う。怖いけど……怖くない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00101",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ええ。姉様は一人じゃない。\n主に私がついてる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00102",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "そう。一人でダメだったら、\nみんなで頑張ればいいんだからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00103",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん……ありがとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00104",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "私も皆さんについていって、\nお手伝いして差し上げたいのですが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_038_00105",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "嬢ちゃんやエルスには諸島同盟の治安を守るって\n大切な仕事があるだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00106",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "安心しなよ、俺が嬢ちゃんの分まで同行して\n航海を成功に導くから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00107",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ジョゼ……ありがたいっすけど、\n本当にいいんすか？　危険な旅になりますよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00108",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺の腕は知ってるでしょ？\nそう易々とやられたりなんかしない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00109",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それに、俺は賞金稼ぎだからね。\n危険な香りに惹かれちまうのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00110",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "なんか、食虫植物に誘われる虫みたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00111",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "もう少し美しいたとえにしてもらいたかったが、\nまあなんでもいいさ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00112",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さんは本当に変てこですね。\nでも……無事に帰ってきてくださいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_038_00113",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、大丈夫だ。嬢ちゃんは俺の帰るべき\n諸島同盟を守っていておくれ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00114",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "じゃあ、道具を削るとして……\nこっちのやつは、魔物の陽動に使うから絶対必要で――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00115",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "これはまあ、なくても大丈夫かな……\n持っていくのはこれくらいでどうすか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00116",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、これなら過不足なし、\nちょうどいいんじゃなかろうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00117",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "よかった！　やっぱ一人で悩むより、\nみんなに相談したほうが解決するっすね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00118",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "これで道具はばっちり！　待ってろ暗黒の氷海！\nよーしベップ！　魔物退治に行きましょ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00119",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "あら、また修行？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00120",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん、総仕上げ！　調合続きで戦いの腕が\nなまっちゃったらいけないしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00121",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様に、ついてく。どこまでも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00122",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]